      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p>This bill reduces the required aggregate market value of voting and non-voting common equity shares for an issuer of securities to qualify as a well-known seasoned issuer. A <em>well-known seasoned issuer</em> is allowed to make expedited public offerings of securities through automatic shelf registrations.</p>",
